she was the one that came on to me.

1:23:24.888 --> 1:23:27.489
- You're a fucking liar!
- No, Matthew. She's the liar!

1:23:27.621 --> 1:23:31.989
She's the fucking liar!
All girls are the same.

1:23:32.455 --> 1:23:35.256
All of them. You can't trust them!

1:23:35.821 --> 1:23:39.522
And look, I am sorry.
I am really, really sorry.

1:23:39.655 --> 1:23:45.089
OK? Because you... You're my best mate
in the whole fucking world.

1:23:45.589 --> 1:23:47.290
I haven't got anyone else.

1:23:47.422 --> 1:23:51.821
I would do anything for you, Matthew,
anything. I would die for you, man.

1:23:55.688 --> 1:23:58.555
Come on, Matthew, shake my hand.

1:24:00.189 --> 1:24:01.621
Matthew, please!

1:24:07.256 --> 1:24:09.223
