1:24:09.356 --> 1:24:11.455
I fucking love you.

1:24:12.223 --> 1:24:13.923
Fucking love you, man.

1:25:06.290 --> 1:25:07.521
Rez? Rez?

1:25:16.023 --> 1:25:17.655
Amen!

1:28:22.223 --> 1:28:24.023
Oh.

1:28:26.588 --> 1:28:28.822
You're never gonna forget this moment.

1:28:29.554 --> 1:28:32.689
I fucking hate you, Kearney!

1:28:35.290 --> 1:28:37.421
Best mates.

1:29:06.156 --> 1:29:10.689
So, Matthew,
how do you feel?

1:29:19.089 --> 1:29:21.023
Well...

1:29:21.923 --> 1:29:24.956
..if you can't tell us how you feel...

1:29:27.454 --> 1:29:29.488
