Matthew, what happened?

1:30:11.421 --> 1:30:13.454
I don't know.

1:30:21.522 --> 1:30:24.089
Jen...

1:30:24.222 --> 1:30:25.722
I'm sorry.

1:30:29.322 --> 1:30:30.689
For everything.

1:30:33.555 --> 1:30:35.722
I was wrong.

1:30:40.056 --> 1:30:41.522
Are you OK?

1:30:42.421 --> 1:30:46.322
I'm fine, Matthew. You know that.

1:30:47.589 --> 1:30:51.789
I'm going to go travelling
for a little while. I leave next week.

1:30:53.023 --> 1:30:55.889
I think it's better
if I'm just not here for a bit, you know

1:31:25.023 --> 1:31:30.656
I'm sorry...
about your car and everything.

1:31:32.656 --> 1:31:35.188
You're defined by what you do, Matthew.

1:31:36.289 --> 1:31:38.522
You make your choices.

1:31:51.722 --> 1:31:54.089
Let's get in there.

1:32:12.756 --> 1:32:15.522
<i>People say a lot of things.</i>

1:32:17.289 --> 1:32:20.889
<i>But it's up to you to decide
what's right or wrong.</i>

1:32:21.622 --> 1:32:23.789
<i>Only you.</i>

1:32:27.822 --> 1:32:30.689
<i>That summer may have changed everything.</i>

